Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.16,0:51:31.76,English,,0,0,0,,Grand secret The Grand reveal all the semester\N{\rChinese}大秘密：大揭示整个学期
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.76,0:51:35.46,English,,0,0,0,,all this course is this the real power the real power of war it's not\N{\rChinese}这一课的全部内容就是战争的真正力量，真正的战争力量不是战争本身，而是战争的战争，它是战争，它是战争，它是战争，你在世界上的货币不是金钱，
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.46,0:51:38.84,English,,0,0,0,,war it's war it's war it's war it's war Your currency in the world is not money,\N{\rChinese}war it's war it's war it's war it's warYour currency in the world is not money,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.34,0:51:43.02,English,,0,0,0,,it is human consciousness.\N{\rChinese}它是人类意识。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.42,0:51:47.74,English,,0,0,0,,Or basically attention.\N{\rChinese}或者说是注意力。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.24,0:51:54.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? This is it, guys, okay?\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是了，大家，好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.58,0:51:58.02,English,,0,0,0,,Once you understand this idea, you understand everything.\N{\rChinese}一旦你理解了这个想法，你就理解了一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.02,0:52:00.72,English,,0,0,0,,But this is a hard idea to understand, so\N{\rChinese}但这个想法很难理解，所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.72,0:52:04.00,English,,0,0,0,,I'll need some time to actually explain this, alright?\N{\rChinese}我需要一点时间来真正解释它，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.46,0:52:08.12,English,,0,0,0,,This war is being fought\N{\rChinese}这场战争正在进行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.12,0:52:13.40,English,,0,0,0,,to control the consciousness of the human race,\N{\rChinese}为了掌控人类的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.54,0:52:16.44,English,,0,0,0,,because it is our consciousness that creates reality itself.\N{\rChinese}因为正是我们的意识创造了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.84,0:52:21.16,English,,0,0,0,,That's the source of all wealth and all power in this world, okay?\N{\rChinese}那是这个世界所有财富和力量的源泉，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.26,0:52:22.72,English,,0,0,0,,That's why this is happening.\N{\rChinese}这就是事情发生的原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.92,0:52:26.94,English,,0,0,0,,In other words, this is a war not just for Iran,\N{\rChinese}换句话说，这场战争不只是为了伊朗。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:29.12,English,,0,0,0,,this is a war not just for the Middle East,\N{\rChinese}这是一场不只是中东的战争，
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.24,0:52:32.22,English,,0,0,0,,it is a war for the soul of humanity.\N{\rChinese}它是一场为人类灵魂而战的战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.92,0:52:34.22,English,,0,0,0,,This is what's happening, guys.\N{\rChinese}这就是现在发生的事，大家。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.90,0:52:37.76,English,,0,0,0,,Alright, this is what World War III is.\N{\rChinese}好了，三战的样子就是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.94,0:52:42.40,English,,0,0,0,,World War III is meant to be the last and final war of all human history,\N{\rChinese}三战本是人类历史上最后一次大冲突，
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.30,0:52:48.10,English,,0,0,0,,because whoever win this war will control the very soul of human existence,\N{\rChinese}谁赢了它，谁就掌握了人类存在的灵魂。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.38,0:52:50.12,English,,0,0,0,,for all eternity, okay?\N{\rChinese}为永恒而已，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.22,0:52:51.44,English,,0,0,0,,That is the end game.\N{\rChinese}这就是终局。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:54.86,English,,0,0,0,,And I know this is a hard idea to understand,\N{\rChinese}我知道这很难懂。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.26,0:52:58.50,English,,0,0,0,,but as we go along, I will explain this to you.\N{\rChinese}但随着进展，我会向你们解释这一点。
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.78,0:53:02.98,English,,0,0,0,,That is the grand secret behind the world.\N{\rChinese}那就是世界背后的大秘密。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.16,0:53:06.56,English,,0,0,0,,And every night, you believe, every night, that, every night, everything that you see today, it's all an illusion.\N{\rChinese}每晚，你相信，每晚，你认为，今天你看到的一切，都是幻觉。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.62,0:53:10.68,English,,0,0,0,,The reality, the truth is\N{\rChinese}现实，真相是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.68,0:53:15.36,English,,0,0,0,,that consciousness is a source of all power of reality itself\N{\rChinese}意识是现实自身所有力量的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.36,0:53:20.44,English,,0,0,0,,and so this is a war for human consciousness,\N{\rChinese}于是这是一场人类意识的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.72,0:53:23.22,English,,0,0,0,,it's a war for the very soul of humanity.\N{\rChinese}这是一场为人类灵魂而战的战争。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.54,0:53:26.48,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Any questions?\N{\rChinese}好的？还有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.58,0:53:30.78,English,,0,0,0,,Alright, I will see you guys next week.\N{\rChinese}好的，我下周见你们。
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.30,0:53:35.70,English,,0,0,0,,Bye.\N{\rChinese}再见
